  <summary date="2023-08-17T14:17:12Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Traveler's Gun Rights Act

This bill allows an individual who does not have a physical residence in a state to use the address for a private mailbox or post office box maintained by that individual for purposes of obtaining a firearm from a federally licensed dealer.</summary>
